mappedTerm: Annual mass drug administration (MDA) with praziquantel and albendazole before the peak transmission season of schistosomiasis (November/December)
Annual MDA with praziquantel and albendazole after the peak transmission season of schistosomiasis (March/April)
Two yearly treatments before and after peak transmission of schistosomiasis (November/December and March/April)
Annual MDA with praziquantel and albendazole before peak transmission of schistosomiasis (November/December), coupled with chemical snail control using niclosamide.
